&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The diagnostics team has been expanded and further developed to drive the diagnostics agenda across the region through the fostering of effective relationships with both providers, commissioners and systems. The immediate aims of the team are to improve patient access and the quality of care to support both COVID-19 recovery and the delivery of key medium to long term objectives aligned to regional and national priorities. The duties of this post are&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; to provide project management support to the Diagnostic Recovery Pathology team. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
